Name: Super Cucho
About the game: About the game Hardcore platformer about a big-eyed toad named Cucho. One morning a hungry cat woke up a toad. Cucho, having discovered that the cat food is over, goes to the supermarket. On the way, he met a magical power that moved him to an unknown world. The player has to help Cucho return home and feed his arrogant pet. Key Features 4 planets and 1 space platform Learn new abilities Epic Boss fights Nice drum and bass soundtrack Sloth!
